### 7.10 Add to Section 8 (Phase 1 Scope) — Future Work Items

> *Not validated in Phase 1 (documented as future work):*
> - *PFCP session event subscription for dynamic TEID discovery from the SMF*
> - *Multi-slice concurrent isolation (architectural guarantee validated in Phase 2)*
> - *Multi-queue RSS-mapped AF_XDP scaling with per-thread Wasm instances*
> - *AF_XDP-to-AF_XDP direct reinjection bypass (eliminating veth traversal overhead)*
> - *Inner 5-tuple secondary filter for sub-TEID exception routing granularity*
